This is the FAQ for the Linux From Scratch "family" of projects.

Despite its location and name, it may contain questions and answers from all
the LFS mailing lists and IRC channel and whatever else. The only limit is that
questions actually be frequently asked.

Information on rendering this document to HTML is in the Makefile.

Information concerning the FAQ itself is in the FAQ. Automatically generated
HTML is available at http://www.linuxfromscratch.org/faq/ Please use this URL
when referencing the FAQ on mailing lists and such.

